data.description: No need to look any further- 11 Essington Lane is calling your name! This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home has so much to offer. Worried about space for your family and friends when entertaining? The highly-functional 4 bed, 3 bath floor plan allows space for everyone! Concerned about the heat of Florida summers? The newly resurfaced saltwater pool will keep you cool (& for the chilly days- it's solar heated!). Don't miss your chance to see 11 Essington Lane by booking your private showing today!
